Package: CVA2.0
Title: Climate Vulnerability Assessment 2.0 Model Builing and Analysis Methods
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Katherine", "Gallagher", , "katherine.gallagher@noaa.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package performs all of the necessary analysis for CVA2.0. This includes pulling and formatting the necessary MOM^ and fisheries data; building and predicting component and ensemble models; calculating exposure from model predictions; and calculating and bootstrapping sensitivity from expert scores. 
